istered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rubella-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 0</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRubellaLowIncidenceVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20more|20than|20or|20equal|20to|2012|20months-42\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageismorethanorequalto12months-42\">Client's age is more than or equal to 12 months-42</a></td><td>Client's age is more than or equal to 12 months</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" ≥ 12 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRubellaLowIncidenceVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20last|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nolivevaccinewasadministeredinthelast4weeks-92\">No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>No live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date - latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) ≥ 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRubellaLowIncidenceVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20due|20for|20rubella|20vaccination-44\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Clientisdueforrubellavaccination-44\">Client is due for rubella vaccination-44</a></td><td>Client is due for rubella vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTRubellaLowIncidenceVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IM